Great way to level, but I think I want my Epic as easy as possible...</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="hgmessage.asp?Guide=126">Post a Message</A></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="hunting.asp">Browse other guides</A></font></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="submithg.asp">Submit a Hunting Guide</A></font></td></tr></div></center>
       
